  "instagram": [
    {
      "date": "Mar 2026",
      "text": "𝗝𝗖𝗖 𝟰 𝗠𝗲𝗲𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 \n\nOn 8 June 2026, the Fourth Joint Coordination Committee (JCC) Meeting for the SATREPS international research project was held at the JST Annex Building in Tokyo, Japan. \n\nThe event began with opening speeches by Prof. Dr. Zahriladha Zakaria, Deputy Vice-Chancellor (Research & Innovation) of Universiti Teknikal Malaysia Melaka (UTeM), Prof. Ir. Dr. Vigna Kumaran A/L Ramachandaramurthy, Deputy Vice-Chancellor (Research & Innovation) of Universiti Tenaga Nasional",
      "image": "images/social/ig/01.jpg"
    },
    {
      "date": "Feb 2026",
      "text": "From 31 May to 5 June 2026, the International Conference on Lightning Protection (ICLP 2026) was held in Sapporo, Japan. \n\nA total of 10 papers from our project were presented at the conference: 4 from Kindai University, 4 from UTeM, and 2 from UNITEN. \n\nOverall, it was a great opportunity for us to share the latest findings from our project with the international community. Congratulations to all participants, especially our team members, for their hard work and commitment i",
      "image": "images/social/ig/02.jpg"
    },
    {
      "date": "Feb 2026",
      "text": "From 31 May to 5 June 2026, the International Conference on Lightning Protection (ICLP 2026) was held in Sapporo, Japan. \n\nA total of 10 papers from our project were presented at the conference: 4 from Kindai University, 4 from UTeM, and 2 from UNITEN. \n\nOverall, it was a great opportunity for us to share the latest findings from our project with the international community. Congratulations to all participants, especially our team members, for their hard work and commitment i",
      "image": "images/social/ig/03.jpg"
    },
    {
      "date": "Jan 2026",
      "text": "✨ 𝗥𝗧𝗟 𝗖𝗮𝗺𝗽𝗮𝗶𝗴𝗻 𝗶𝗻 𝗠𝗲𝗹𝗮𝗸𝗮, 𝗠𝗮𝗹𝗮𝘆𝘀𝗶𝗮 – 𝗣𝗮𝗿𝘁 𝟭 ✨\n\nOn April 27, 2026, researchers from Kindai University arrived at the RTL site, UiTM Jasin Campus, for the campaign. This is to attempt the first time RTL in Malaysia. \n\nToday, we carried out preparations to test a new rocket developed by UiTM Shah Alam at the site. Overall, the preparation went well. \n\nA big thank you to the participants from UiTM Jasin, UiTM Shah Alam, UTeM, and the students for their support and assistance thro",
      "image": "images/social/ig/04.jpg"
    },
    {
      "date": "Nov 2025",
      "text": "✨ 𝗘𝗶𝗱 𝗠𝘂𝗯𝗮𝗿𝗮𝗸! ✨ 𝗦𝗲𝗹𝗮𝗺𝗮𝘁 𝗛𝗮𝗿𝗶 𝗥𝗮𝘆𝗮 𝗔𝗶𝗱𝗶𝗹𝗳𝗶𝘁𝗿𝗶 ✨\".",
      "image": "images/social/ig/05.jpg"
    },
    {
      "date": "Oct 2025",
      "text": "⚡️ 𝗜𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿𝗻𝗮𝗹 𝗟𝗶𝗴𝗵𝘁𝗻𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗦𝗲𝗺𝗶𝗻𝗮𝗿 𝟱 ⚡️\n \nOn 13 February 2026, the fifth seminar in this series was successfully held in person at the THOR Lab, UTeM. The session covered lightning localization, corona discharge, and rocket-triggered lightning (RTL). \n\n𝙋𝙧𝙚𝙨𝙚𝙣𝙩𝙖𝙩𝙞𝙤𝙣𝙨 𝙬𝙚𝙧𝙚 𝙙𝙚𝙡𝙞𝙫𝙚𝙧𝙚𝙙 𝙗𝙮:\n•Mr. Nabil Ehsan (MSc Candidate, UNITEN) — shared current progress on lightning localization using Malaysian FALMA data, including 2D and 3D mapping. \n• Mr. Rifhan (PhD Candidate, UTeM) — presented a",
      "image": "images/social/ig/06.jpg"
    },
    {
      "date": "Sep 2025",
      "text": "𝗘𝗾𝘂𝗶𝗽𝗺𝗲𝗻𝘁 𝗛𝗮𝗻𝗱𝗲𝗱 𝗢𝘃𝗲𝗿\nA batch of equipment which arrived recently has been handed over to UTeM. The equipment was Data Center, Current Sensors, as well as LF and VHF Receivers. Deputy Vice Chancellor of the university, Professor Dr. Zahriladha Bin Zakaria, signed the Hand-Over Certificate in his office. With the Data Center, we can see lightning real-time. ∎\".",
      "image": "images/social/ig/07.jpg"
    },
    {
      "date": "Aug 2025",
      "text": "𝗠𝗶𝗱𝘁𝗲𝗿𝗺 𝗘𝘃𝗮𝗹𝘂𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻 – 𝗣𝗮𝗿𝘁 𝟰 (𝗧𝗵𝗲 𝗗𝗮𝘆) \n𝗠𝗲𝗲𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴𝘀 𝘄𝗶𝘁𝗵 𝗝𝗦𝗧, 𝗝𝗜𝗖𝗔, 𝗠𝗢𝗛𝗘 & 𝗦𝗶𝘁𝗲 𝗩𝗶𝘀𝗶𝘁 𝘁𝗼 𝗠𝗘𝗧 𝗞𝘂𝗮𝗹𝗮 𝗣𝗶𝗹𝗮𝗵\n\nOn 9 February, we were joined by two representatives from JST — Prof. Tamura and Mr. Furukawa for the first agenda of the day. \n\nThe day began with our team travelling to JICA Malaysia Office for a meeting with representatives from JST, JICA, and the Japanese researchers. The session included important discussions on project progress, collaboration, and future planning. \n\nAft",
      "image": "images/social/ig/08.jpg"
    },
